sentences: Michael "Manse" Hansen (born 17 October 1990) is a Swedish DJ and record producer.
He became known throughout Sweden when he placed second in a remix contest of the song "Escape" by 3LAU along with Paris & Simo.
He became known for numerous remixes from 2013 to 2014 before releasing his own singles from 2015.
